ActConstitution Act, 1867
SubjectAdministrator of the Government of Saskatchewan
PrecisAppointment to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of SASKATCHEWAN (1) the Hon. Neal W. Caldwell from June 24 to 27, 2013, inclusive; (2) the Hon. Lian M. Schwann from July 2 to 7, 2013, inclusive; (3) the Hon. Maurice J. Herauf July 8 to 21, 2013, inclusive; (4) the Hon. Donna L. Wilson from July 22 to 28, 2013, inclusive, (5) the Hon. Ted C. Zarzeczny from July 29 to August 4, 2013, inclusive; (6) the Hon. Ralph K. Ottenbreit from August 5 to 11, 2013, inclusive; (7) the Hon. Neal W. Caldwell from August 12 to 18, 2013, inclusive; (8) the Hon. Ralph K. Ottenbreit August 19 to 25, 2013, inclusive; (9) the Hon. Neal W. Caldwell from August 26 to September 6, 2013, inclusive; and (10) the Hon. Robert G. Richards effective September 7, 2013.
